  <summary date="2021-02-26T15:23:45Z" status="Introduced in House">End Dark Money Act

This bill repeals in FY2021 the restriction on the use of funds by the Internal Revenue Service to issue any regulation or guidance relating to the standard for determining whether certain nonprofit civic organizations are being operated exclusively for the promotion of social welfare.</summary>
